reviewText: Because it lived up to my expectations. Quality photos of quality subjects. Uplifting experience.
Big fan of Laura Dore. This DVD is disappointing only about 30 minutes and less than I expected, no extras, bonus footage etc. Still a fan of her, but not this particular DVD.
You have to appreciate the beautiful locations this was shot in. No complaints here, its like a mini vacation to the Italian coast on DVD.

first of all i bought 2 dvds from show magazine website so i kinda knew what to expect with this dvd its not a straight out stripping dvd but its a sexy photoshoot dvd how ever the back of the dvd says its 100 minutes long when actualy its only 30 minutes it also says + bouns fotage theres no bouns fotage  save your money if this is what your looking for go to show magazine website store and buy jesikah maximus official dvd vol 1 shes not any sexier than laura but the dvd is a lot hotter

So where it is surely interesting to see the efforts required behind the scenes, there just was not enough of Laura, both in time and in body. The one scene where we could have received a little 'treat' was blurred out. So, not being given the opportunity to enjoy 'more' of this young lady, it would have been nice to get to know more about her as a person. I look forward to perhaps a more in depth experience should she do another video in the future. She has an interesting personality and voice- she should think about a 'femme fatale' role in a movie soon! In the mean time, you may want to borrow this one if you can and spend the money you saved on one of the magazines where she is featured.
